			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">When you forage and dont take the item off your cursor it will stack on your cursor.  All you have to do is, when you get back to the computer you just open a bag and drop each item in a slot.  I have foraged multiple items while in POK running around with out putting the stuff in the bag as soon as i got it.
<br />

<br />
