				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I put ranged attack on one of the hott buttons Let's say I put it on the second button.  Under options and keyboard I made the hot button key to be "Z".  I installed the game pad software and follow the directions above for maping the game pad to the "Z" key (the game pad link still works for me.)  Now when I push the game pad buttion I mapped to the "Z" key it automatically does what is on the 2nd hot key button.  If I want to track non stop or forage  non stop I make sure the correct hot key is mapped to "Z".
<br />

