				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">any function of the keyboard can be duplicated by the N50 Speedpad  meaning with the configuration software that comes with the device you can make the keys, scroll, or D-Pad, work like specific keyboard commands or multiple commands (macro's).  So if you truly wanted to you could map the Kick,disarm, taunt, sense heading all to 1 key on the N50.  so that every time you pressed it in a fight you would Kick, try to disarm, taunt, and Sense the direction you are headed in.
<br />

<br />
One configuration of  keys could allow you to auto target the nearst NPC, yourself, move &lt;,&gt;,^,v, auto range attck, kick, auto forage, auto drag corpse, and auto spam group chat for languages.  But there are endless possibilities, this is simply one suggestin and an effort to explain some of what this nice device can do.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=623266" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.digikitten.com/playhousev2/files/Ranger_lahru/smrusg2.png" border="0" /></a>
